'''線上撲克（{{lang-en|Online poker}}）'''顧名思義就是在[[網際網路|網際網路]]上的[[撲克|撲克]]遊戲。網上撲克的玩家數在全世界持續上升，Christiansen Capital Advisors指出網上撲克的收益已從2001年的8270萬美元升至2005年的24億美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsweek.com/id/56438 |title=Going All In For Online Poker |publisher=Newsweek |date=2005-08-15 |accessdate=2009-03-19 |archive-date=2010-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212081654/http://www.newsweek.com/id/56438 |dead-url=no }}</ref>DrKW and Global Betting and Gaming Consultants於2004年的統計是14億美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://us.ft.com/ftgateway/superpage.ft?news_id=fto062720050064003754 |title=Financial Times: Online Poker 2004 revenues and 2008 forecast |publisher=Us.ft.com |date=2003-08-28 |accessdate=2009-03-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090520074854/http://us.ft.com/ftgateway/superpage.ft?news_id=fto062720050064003754 |archivedate=2009-05-20 }}</ref>  美國會計師行[[Joseph_Eve,_Certified_Public_Accountants|Joseph Eve, Certified Public Accountants]]在聽證會上表示，估計博彩注碼中有1/4是網上下注的<ref name=Joseph>{{cite web|last=Eve|first=Grant|title=Grant Eve Testimony 111711 - United States Senate Committee on Indian Affairs|url=http://www.indian.senate.gov/hearings/loader.cfm?csModule=security/getfile&pageid=9698|work=The Future of Internet Gaming|accessdate=11 January 2013|archive-date=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515021233/http://www.indian.senate.gov/hearings/loader.cfm?csModule=security%2Fgetfile&pageid=9698|dead-url=no}}</ref>。網上撲克以[[德州撲克|德州撲克]]為主，亦有奧馬哈等不同版本提供。網上撲克有別於實戰撲克，玩家可以同時玩多局，而且不會被對方透過面部表情試探自己的卡牌，與實戰撲克不同的是，All-in輸了也不會感到尷尬，因此網上撲克玩家的注碼一般都較隨意。

